      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Reap What You Saw",
        "Client": "Clumsy Farmer",
        "Description": "I was having the darndest time trying\r\nto cut my grass\u2014\u0027bout cut my dang\r\nhand off\u2014when I seen the darndest\r\nthing! This darn monster did one li\u0027l twirl\r\nand mowed down just about everything\r\naround it! Maybe if I watch you hunt\r\none, I can figure out how it does that.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Great Izuchi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "On r\u00E9colte ce que l\u0027on s\u00E8me",
        "Client": "Fermier maladroit",
        "Description": "Je coupais l\u0027herbe \u00E0 la faux\r\net j\u0027ai r\u00E9ussi \u00E0 me faire mal !\r\nTu crois que tu pourrais\r\n\u00E9liminer un Grand Izuchi\r\npour moi ? Je pourrais m\u0027inspirer\r\ndes mouvements\r\nde sa queue pour m\u0027am\u00E9liorer.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Grand Izuchi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Mietitura del wyvern roteante",
        "Client": "Contadino maldestro",
        "Description": "Cercavo di falciare l\u0027erba e\r\nmi sono tagliato. Potresti\r\naffrontare un Gran Izuchi per\r\nme? Se osservassi i movimenti\r\ndella sua coda, potrei imparare\r\nqualche trucco su come usare\r\nla falce.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Gran Izuchi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wirbelnde Schnitte",
        "Client": "Tollpatschiger Bauer",
        "Description": "Ich wollte das Gras mit einer\r\nSichel schneiden und stutzte\r\nmich dabei fast selbst zurecht!\r\nDieses verflixte Monster machte\r\neinen kleinen Wirbel und m\u00E4hte\r\nso ziemlich alles in der N\u00E4he\r\nnieder. Hilf mir bitte!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Gro\u00DF-Izuchi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Cosecha wyverna",
        "Client": "Granjero torparr\u00F3n",
        "Description": "Estaba pas\u00E1ndolo fatal segando\r\nla hierba cuando, de repente...\r\n\u00A1fue alucinante! Pas\u00F3 un\r\nmonstruo que con solo mover\r\nla cola lo seg\u00F3 todo alrededor.\r\nSi me cazaras uno, quiz\u00E1\r\npodr\u00EDa ver mejor c\u00F3mo lo hace.",
        "Target": "Caza un Gran Izuchi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
